summary: tony stark, eh? i see you’re a man of culture as well (in all seriousness though whos your favorite marvel character/actor? im a...
question: tony stark, eh? i see you’re a man of culture as well (in all seriousness though whos your favorite marvel character/actor? im a big nerd)
answer:
I’m a massive fan of Marvel!!! I could talk about it for hours and hours.

My favorite character is between Iron Man, Dr. Strange and Spider-Man. I have plenty of favorite actors (they’re all just too good), but I’ll have to go down to my favorites Tom Holland, RDJ, and my absolute biggest man crush ever Chris Evans.

title: Avengers 4 Fan Theory Reshapes Thanos' Daughter Nebula!
body:

A new Avengers 4 fan theory sees Thanos’ daughter Nebula transformed from the walking cybernetic version we’ve come to see in the Marvel Cinematic Universe specifically in Guardians of the Galaxy and Avengers: Infinity War into a flesh and blood version.

The theory comes from Reddit user Leighgion:
